author: Ed Kilgore
title: A Black Politician’s Trump Endorsement Raises Eyebrows But Won’t Move Votes
description: Aside from the occasional endorsement from random black politicians, there’s no real evidence that Trump’s appeal to black voters has improved much.
content: Nothing excites the pro-Trump media quite like an African-American public figure endorsing the Boss. On the rare occasion it happens, there is much excitement about this being the tip of an emerging iceberg of black support for the man who Made America Great … [+5474 chars]
